overview: Ty Fox returns under a new name, J. Steele. You are treated to a bevy of delectable, Jet Set-flavored, muscled studs in a series of serial threeways.  Exclusive J. Steele dominates this all-muscle video featuring some of the hottest studs in the business. If you like beef on your men - look no further.  Jet Set Muscle is all about personal training at your best. And while they are getting sweaty, prepare to oil yourself up to the hot action of these muscle-gods.
title: Jet Set Muscle
